            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "FI專欄｜3分鐘「取回」屬於你的退休金｜Jan Wong",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"FI專欄｜3分鐘「取回」屬於你的退休金｜Jan Wong\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qIaVh25Ebk.IBpx67YMjJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/11d7c2c0bfeea6f10bb847b67de0590b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">FI專欄｜3分鐘「取回」屬於你的退休金｜Jan Wong</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">想像一下你換過幾份工，強積金戶口散落在不同銀行和保險公司。平日忙到飛起，誰會記得逐間查詢？結果退休那天才發現十幾二十年的血汗錢分散在不同的供應商，甚至部分早已「失蹤」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至2021年底，全港有13.8萬個合資格但無人提取的MPF帳戶，總額高達63億元，平均每個帳戶約4.3萬元。這些錢正默默被管理費侵蝕，年復一年，原本屬於你的退休儲備，就這樣白白流走。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去找回戶口、整合、再提取，動輒要打幾通電話、填幾份表，花上幾星期。現在，積金易（eMPF）平台徹底改變一切。你只需3分鐘，用手機就能一次過找回所有MPF戶口。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-297593c7-f16f-3edd-9225-766e325ebbbd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">超簡單三步驟：<br/> 1. 下載「智方便」同「積金易」App<br/> 2. 註冊智方便（用香港身份證幾分鐘完成）<br/> 3. 用智方便一鍵登入積金易</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1)</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TdJY9iLALK9_5y61roVnyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTIxMDtoPTIxMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/7471965bd7d245f59e6c515393077865\" width=\"150\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2)</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/riqScJiu4TVy_tFmhPIwJA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTIxMDtoPTIxMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/1d54992c8e02d3a768435b3c7b6ec9f2\" width=\"150\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">登入後，所有散落在不同供應商的個人帳戶、現職供款戶口一目了然。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最近我幫一位退休叔叔註冊，結果發現他名下還有接近7萬元從未提取。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">打工仔，別讓自己的血汗錢變成他人養分。趁平台已全面運作，花3分鐘檢查一下，可能即時多幾萬蚊退休本錢。你的退休生活，值得自己親手掌握。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MPF的事情上需要處理的朋友歡迎點擊以下連結👇🏻</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">🔗<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://l1nk.dev/m95n2mg;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://l1nk.dev/m95n2mg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://l1nk.dev/m95n2mg</a></p></div>",
